  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The freestanding internally illuminated advertisement display unit is prominently sited on the forecourt of 320 Caledondian Road and constitutes an excess of illumination on the premises. In conjunction with existing signage, it results in clutter to the detriment of the visual amenity and character of this part of the Barnsbury Conservation Area. The advertisement is thereby contrary to Policy D33 of Islington's Revised Unitary Development Plan as agreed by the Council in December 2001."
